name: Tripezi
overview: Tripezi is a trusted and increasing online marketplace that you can use to rent or list a Spare room,Apartment, House, Villa or any other kind of property people might like to stay in. Book a Tripezi property in one of the destinations worldwide or list your place to make some money while you’re away you ca book a unique, perfect and comfortable place to stay at www.tripezi.com. Make money by renting out your place or Save money by booking with Tripezi (your alternative to expensive hotel rooms)
